Class Trip

java.lang.Object
  location.Trip
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Trip
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

A Trip represents a complete journey which contains a set of Paths. A Trip is completed when two Path are with in 0.080km or 80m of each other.

Author:
Matthew Schmidt
